# Build Dashboard Application

Create a new interactive dashboard for monitoring workflows

## Generated by Agentic SDLC

This project was automatically generated by the Agentic SDLC system.

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build

# Preview production build
npm run preview

# Run tests
npm test

# Lint code
npm run lint
```

## Tech Stack

- **React 18** - UI library
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
- **Vite** - Build tool and dev server
- **Vitest** - Unit testing
- **ESLint** - Code linting
